      <title>泰国富豪押注中美争端将缓解曼谷房地产市场过剩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/thai-scion-bets-us-china-feud-will-ease-bangkok-property-glut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由泰国首富控制的星狮地产有限公司 (Frasers Property Ltd.) 正借助中美紧张局势缓解困扰泰国首都的办公空间供应过剩问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/thai-scion-bets-us-china-feud-will-ease-bangkok-property-glut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 05:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
